sections.TOP: Lord Paramount of the Westerlands06882mewjzyjpe71nehpspjryctesca3n00h1774812015-03-17T04:41:47ZSharp Blades26158496'''Lord Paramount of the Westerlands''' is the title given to the ruler of [[the Westerlands]] in ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]''. The holder is typically the head of the Westerlands' [[Great House]], which since the title's creation during the [[Wars of Conquest]] has been [[House Lannister]].
